I. AM. SO. EXCITED.

These are some of the best flight deals that we have been seeing this week, a lot of the dates in June were skyrocketing pretty fast...so if you are hoping to come with, it is probably not a bad idea to purchase soon! The couple days surrounding this particular flight were also similarly priced options - it would be fantastic to fly out together!! But is nice that this time frame still seems to be reasonably priced if we end up on different flights within the same couple days
May 8-17th
It is a United flight our of Newark through Oslo and then onto Trondheim!

Rough Sketch of the Trip: Fly into Trondheim, train up to Bodo, car/ferry to Lofoten, other hiking adventures, train back down to Trondheim, fly home.
Justus and I are hoping to book the flights soon so that we don't miss out on the deal...most other flights are in the 650-780 range in May, June and August
May seems to be the best prices and while it is kinda of a tricky work month for me, May 8th-17th actually would work! We can keep tabs on flights from Detroit to NYC/JFK over the next while
After a lot of research, Justus and I found a pretty good flight from JFK to Trondheim - - https://goo.gl/flights/YJox
